data.description: Discover the perfect home that combines style, function, and a country location in one irresistible package. Located in the coveted Loreauville school district, this home has it all. The majority of the home includes modern updates and perfectly combines old and new, with fresh paint colors, vinyl plank flooring, granite and quartz.  And the ceilings...oh how we love the ceilings. The property also includes spacious workshop that is perfect for hobbyists or extra storage, but what truly sets this home apart is its serene location right on the bayou.  Framed by two beautiful oaks and the perfect tree swing, this home is calling your name! Contact your agent and schedule your showing today.
